'''旗鱼目'''（Istiophoriformes）是目前尚未[[生物分类学|生物分类学]]完全承认的一个[[硬骨鱼|硬骨鱼]][[目_(生物)|目]]。一些定义中只包括现存的两个统称'''尖嘴鱼'''（billfish）的[[科_(生物)|科]]——[[剑旗鱼科|剑旗鱼科]]和[[旗鱼科|旗鱼科]]<ref name = eol>{{cite web | url = http://eol.org/pages/42342994/overview | title = Istiophoriformes | access-date = 10 May 2018 | publisher = Encyclopedia of Life | archive-date = 2018-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180630162054/http://eol.org/pages/42342994/overview | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而另一些定义则还包括[[金梭鱼科|金梭鱼科]]<ref name = Nelson5>{{cite web | url = https://81a86d48-a-62cb3a1a-s-sites.googlegroups.com/site/fotw5th/home/FotW5Classification.pdf?attachauth=ANoY7crnPmFXqnJpmRlpzLSdqx8GmsCmFXNBj8fAYuPuhFBvCfHo4TahH7eM_yruTzHI27nZRRWWJPRR7U9HopPBRlQK8iW_73EG6FVke6aUjl20fgZXiChDnl-xqMl4L2I-wHwV7D4qcPAQI1vSV6YfFYAm5qb7t5w0rJ_ierkZ91ezIvpQ_5f0kSbFiUx-YYGXP1US1GbwSf-G7sRx4XEikm73VqVA0idVnlkaFjzI53bkuIQY0OQ%3D&attredirects=0 | title = Classification of fishes from Fishes of the World 5th Edition | author1 = Nelson, JS | author2 = Grande, TC | author3 = Wilson, MVH | name-list-style = amp | year = 2016 | access-date = 10 May 2018 | archive-date = 2020-03-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200313140909/https://81a86d48-a-62cb3a1a-s-sites.googlegroups.com/site/fotw5th/home/FotW5Classification.pdf?attachauth=ANoY7coP7L850hc2KblijBZWJQpzKfQY5GAjnopzwval2xwnqist9WExZkxt7SF4OvVwR9AV965qa40-EYcVHCT05XcutxECBaraK4JiAiyzAxdDFtfYwmxnc4qgd7WRfrmAa9Tcd7C54K_LSySz6efxuNIrxKbUgiBWoJRxaW5HwFGnsUfIyPF6xng6Po7_GYRbA0tP9UW-XtL1aWLcrBineCR5HtI3Up70XgyfXNc6fAtPJOyGe5s%3D&attredirects=1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

旗鱼目下属的[[物种|物种]]都是[[海洋|海洋]]中位居[[食物链|食物链]]上层的大型[[掠食性|掠食性]][[咸水鱼|咸水鱼]]，一些種類可超過{{convert|4|m}}長，[[吻突|吻部]]細長，短距离游泳速度极快，是非常受歡迎的[[食用鱼|食用鱼]]和[[遊釣魚|遊釣魚]]。

